ers a positive crew environment \u2013 the combination most aligned with safe, long\u2011haul operations.\n**Therefore I support Candidate\u202fC as the best overall fit.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
